OL,3,CPolice name man stabbed to death
OL,5,FA man who was stabbed to death in a
OL,6,FLincolnshire town has been named as 37-
OL,7,Fyear-old Danny Fowler.
OL,9,FPolice were called to Union Street in
OL,10,FMarket Rasen just after 5pm on
OL,11,FThursday 12 March to reports Mr Fowler
OL,12,Fhad been attacked.
OL,14,FHe died later in hospital and a post
OL,15,Fmortem confirmed he had died of
OL,16,Fseveral stab wounds.
OL,18,FThree people - a 55-year-old man, a 29-
OL,19,Fyear-old man and a 31-year-old woman -
OL,20,Fhave been arrested on suspicion of
OL,21,Fmurder.
